import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"mri-prod-theme"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#mri-prod-theme"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`MRI PROD \${theme}`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`打包 \${theme} 的生产环境代码`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-bash"}}>{`\$ mri prod social
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag></MDXTag>
